1. Given a list of Integers, where every number appears an even number of times in the list, except for one number that appears an odd number of times in the list,
write readable, sustainable code that finds the number which appears an odd number of times in the list.

2.Given you have 11 coins, that all weigh exactly the same, except for one - this one is heavier.
Given you have a balance scale - similar to what the goddess of justice has in her hand.
Write readable and sustainable code that finds the heavy coin.
